'''亨利維爾'''（{{lang|en|'''Henryville'''}}）為[[美國|美國]][[印第安納州|印第安納州]][[克拉克縣_(印地安納州)|克拉克縣]]{{le|門羅鎮區 (印第安納州克拉克縣)|Monroe Township, Clark County, Indiana|門羅鎮區}}的一座[[普查规定居民点|普查规定居民点]]<ref>{{cite gnis|436039|Henryville, Indiana|2016-10-23}}</ref>。根據[[2010年美國人口普查|2010年美國人口普查]]，此地區人口有1,905人。

{{le|克拉克州立森林|Clark State Forest}}坐落在亨利維爾境內，為印第安納州最早設立的州立森林，另外此地區也是[[肯德基|肯德基]]創始人[[哈兰德·桑德斯|哈兰德·桑德斯]]的故鄉<ref name = ChicagoST20120302/>。

==歷史==
此地區於1850年設立，當時稱'''莫里斯敦'''（Morristown）。後來在1853年更名為現名，以紀念曾在[[威士忌暴乱|威士忌暴乱]]中擔任上校的亨利·弗格森（Henry Ferguson）上校。1840年，亨利·弗格森購買此地區的土地，而後在此地區設立亨利維爾，並幫助說服[[賓夕法尼亞鐵路|賓夕法尼亞鐵路]]官員能讓該鐵路線可通過克拉克縣<ref>{{cite web|url=http://indianapublicmedia.org/momentofindianahistory/henry-ferguson|title=Henry Ferguson|author=Yael Kasander|date=2007-03-12|publisher=Indiana Public Media|accessdate=2012-03-08|archive-date=2020-11-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201118044934/https://indianapublicmedia.org/momentofindianahistory/henry-ferguson/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此地區的郵政局於1865年設立<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.postalhistory.com/postoffices.asp?task=display&state=IN&county=Clark | title=Clark County | publisher=Jim Forte Postal History | accessdate=2014-08-30 | archive-date=2014-09-03 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140903100414/http://www.postalhistory.com/postoffices.asp?task=display&state=IN&county=Clark | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

亨利維爾為[[肯德基|肯德基]]創始人[[哈兰德·桑德斯|哈兰德·桑德斯]]上校的故鄉<ref>{{cite book|last=Witzel|first=Morgen|title=Encyclopedia of History of American Management|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=sOyPumbw0poC&pg=PA447|date=2005-05-15|publisher=A&C Black|isbn=978-1-84371-131-5|page=447|access-date=2016-11-26|archive-date=2019-05-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190513215905/https://books.google.com/books?id=sOyPumbw0poC&pg=PA447|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===2012年龍捲風===
美東時間2012年3月2日下午3時15分許，一個[[改良藤田级数|EF-4級]]的龍捲風襲擊亨利維爾，並對當地造成大規模的損害，而該次災害至少造成3人喪生<ref name = ChicagoST20120302>{{Cite web |url=http://www.suntimes.com/11008354-417/indiana-town-completely-gone-after-tornado-kills-at-least-3-official-says.html |title=Indiana town completely gone after tornado kills at least 3; Sun Times; March 2, 2012. |accessdate=2016-11-26 |archive-date=2014-11-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141129030552/http://www.suntimes.com/11008354-417/indiana-town-completely-gone-after-tornado-kills-at-least-3-official-says.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。該龍捲風的移動路徑長度超過50英里<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.philly.com/philly/hp/news_update/20120304_ap_stormsdemolishsmalltownsinindky38dead.html?c=r|title=Storms demolish small towns in Ind., Ky.; 38 dead|last1=Alford|first1=Roger|author2=Jim Suhr|agency=[[美联社|美联社]]|date=2012-03-04|accessdate=2012-03-04|newspaper=[[費城詢問報|費城詢問報]]}}</ref>。亨利維爾小學（Henryville Elementary School）和{{le|亨利維爾中學|Henryville Jr/Sr High School}}因受到此龍捲風的襲擊而被摧毀<ref>{{cite web |author=Susan Candiotti and Moni Basu |url=http://www.cnn.com/2012/03/03/us/severe-weather-indiana-town/ |title=March tornadoes: One day there was a town; the next day it was gone |publisher=CNN |date=2012-03-03 |accessdate=2012-05-22 |archive-date=2020-08-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200814180817/https://www.cnn.com/2012/03/03/us/severe-weather-indiana-town/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://usnews.msnbc.msn.com/_news/2012/03/03/10569717-crash-bang-break-as-students-staff-survive-twister-hitting-school |title=U.S. News - 'Crash, bang, break' as students, staff survive twister hitting school |publisher=Usnews.msnbc.msn.com |date= |accessdate=2012-05-22 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120527114716/http://usnews.msnbc.msn.com/_news/2012/03/03/10569717-crash-bang-break-as-students-staff-survive-twister-hitting-school |archivedate=2012-05-27 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.cbsnews.com/8301-201_162-57390040/state-of-emergency-declared-in-ind-ky/ |title=Storms demolish small towns in Ind., Ky.; 38 dead |publisher=CBS News |date= |accessdate=2012-05-22 |archive-date=2013-09-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130923200222/http://www.cbsnews.com/8301-201_162-57390040/state-of-emergency-declared-in-ind-ky/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==地理==
亨利維爾坐落在北緯38度32分28秒、西經85度46分0秒（亦可表示成38.541088, -85.766677）<ref name="GR1">{{cite web|url=http://www.census.gov/geo/www/gazetteer/gazette.html|publisher=[[美国人口调查局|美国人口调查局]]|accessdate=2011-04-23|date=2011-02-12|title=US Gazetteer files: 2010, 2000, and 1990|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060720110047/http://www.census.gov/geo/www/gazetteer/gazette.html|archive-date=2006-07-20|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。根據[[美国人口调查局|美国人口调查局]]的資料，此普查规定居民点總面積為{{convert|2.9|sqmi|sqkm|2}}，全境皆為陸地。

===氣候===
夏季炎熱多雨、冬季涼爽乾燥為此地區的氣候特徵。根據[[柯本气候分类法|柯本气候分类法]]，亨利維爾的氣候屬於[[副热带湿润气候|副热带湿润气候]]，氣候圖中簡寫「Cfa」<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.weatherbase.com/weather/weather-summary.php3?s=519321&cityname=Henryville%2C+Indiana%2C+United+States+of+America&units= |title=Climate Summary for Henryville, Indiana |accessdate=2016-11-26 |archive-date=2019-05-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190513043902/http://www.weatherbase.com/weather/weather-summary.php3?s=519321&cityname=Henryville%2C+Indiana%2C+United+States+of+America&units= |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==人口統計==
